Nicegram was updated to Telegram version 9.6.5

Here s what s new in Nicegram: Enhanced AI Assistant: We have introduced new characters to our AI assistant feature. These characters respond based on the selected characteristics providing a more personalized and engaging experience. Whether you prefer a friendly helper or a witty companion our AI assistant has got you covered! Improved Performance: We have made significant optimizations to enhance the overall performance of Nicegram. You can expect faster loading times smoother navigation and a more seamless messaging experience. We are committed to continuously improving our app to ensure a top notch user experience.

Instant Responses: Say goodbye to long waiting times! Our AI assistant Lily now starts typing an answer to your questions immediately providing prompt responses. Enhanced Stability: We ve diligently worked on resolving various bugs and issues ensuring a smoother and more reliable experience for all users. We hope you enjoy these updates and have a seamless experience with the app!
We have fixed some bugs and made performance improvements to enhance your experience with Nicegram messenger. Thank you for using Nicegram!

Updated UI for chatbot: We ve refreshed the design of our chatbot to make it more visually appealing and user friendly. Dark Light themes: We ve added the option for users to choose between a dark or light theme for the app. Message history: We ve introduced a new feature that allows the chatbot Lily to remember previous conversations. Referral gem rewards: We ve added a new referral system that rewards users with gems for referring their friends to Nicegram. We hope you enjoy these new features and updates and thank you for your continued support of Nicegram!

Refined design for the GPT 4 chatbot: We ve made some improvements to the design of our GPT 4 chatbot to make it even more visually appealing and user friendly. Added the GPT 4 chatbot to the onboarding process: We ve added the GPT 4 chatbot to our onboarding process to help users get started with the app more quickly and easily. Bug fixes: We ve fixed some issues that were reported by users which should improve the overall stability and performance of the app. Improved speed: We ve made some optimizations to the app s code to make it run faster and smoother.

Nicegram was updated to Telegram version 9.4 25075 PROFILE PHOTO MAKER: Quickly create group and profile pictures from animated emoji and stickers with the new Set Emoji option. EMOJI CATEGORIES: Filter stickers and emoji by categories like love celebration or sleeping in the sticker and emoji tabs. CHAT TRANSLATION: As a Premium user translate entire chats in real time as you scroll them or receive new messages. NETWORK USAGE: Check how much of your data was spent on Telegram in the updated Network Usage section in Settings. AUTO SAVE INCOMING MEDIA: Adjust which media should be automatically saved to Camera Roll from your chats based on size type and source. MEDIA PERMISSIONS IN GROUPS: Control whether members of your groups can send 9 distinct media types like Photos Voice or Video Messages. TRENDING EMOJI: As a Premium user check out trending emoji packs in the emoji panel and long press an emoji to zoom in. ANNUAL SUBSCRIPTIONS: Save up to 40 by pre paying for a year of Telegram Premium! and we re not done yet SELECT CHATS FOR BOTS: Bot developers can now let users quickly select groups channels or contacts that meet predefined criteria more in BotNews . RE LOGIN WITH APPLE ID: Logged out users can quickly log back in using their Apple ID without entering an SMS code 2 Step Verification password is still required .
In this version we fixed bugs that occurred when updating to the latest version of the Telegram API.

Nicegram was updated to Telegram version 9.3 241534 HIDDEN MEDIA ZERO STORAGE USAGE NEW DRAWING TOOLS PROFILE PICTURES FOR YOUR CONTACTS AND PUPPIES We found someone s letter to Santa and implemented everything on the list: Hidden Media Media with spoiler effects. You can wrap photos and videos you send in a fuzzy cover by selecting media in the attachment menu and tapping Hide With Spoiler. Zero Storage Usage Auto remove cached media. You can choose how long cached media is kept in Private Chats Groups and Channels and add exceptions for specific chats. Removing media by type. Separate tabs with Media Files and Music from all chats let you quickly clear the largest files. Pie charts. The new design helps you see what s taking up space. Dwarves with calculators. Cache size is now calculated a lot faster. Reminder: All cached media you remove remains accessible in the cloud and can be re downloaded if needed. Profile Pictures for Your Contacts Setting pictures for your contacts. You can choose your own picture for a contact only you will see it on their profile. Suggested profile pictures. When editing your contacts you can suggest a photo for their profile. It will take them just two taps to add the picture you suggested. Public profile pictures. If you only allow certain users to see your profile photos you can set a public picture for everyone else. Ultimate profile picture privacy. You can set Who can see my profile photos to Nobody and add some users or groups as exceptions. Hiding Members in Large Groups Member list privacy. Owners of large groups can hide the list of members. The letter also mentioned taking over the world and a puppy but we hope the real Santa will be able to handle that now that we ve done the rest.
